import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"welcome-to-react-native-share"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#welcome-to-react-native-share"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Welcome to React Native Share`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://circleci.com/gh/react-native-community/react-native-share/tree/master"}}><MDXTag name="img" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"src":"https://circleci.com/gh/react-native-community/react-native-share/tree/master.svg?style=svg&circle-token=0c6860240abba4e16bd07df0ea805a72b67b8d41","alt":"CircleCI"}}></MDXTag></MDXTag>{` `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"http://badge.fury.io/js/react-native-share"}}><MDXTag name="img" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"src":"https://badge.fury.io/js/react-native-share.svg","alt":"npm version"}}></MDXTag></MDXTag>{`
Share Social , Sending Simple Data to Other Apps`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p"><MDXTag name="em" components={components} parentName="strong">{`NOTE: React Native now implements share functionality `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="em" props={{"href":"https://facebook.github.io/react-native/docs/share.html"}}>{`Read more`}</MDXTag></MDXTag></MDXTag></MDXTag></MDXTag>
